Constance Zimmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constance_Zimmer 0 Constance Zimmer (born October 11, 1970) is an American actress. She is best known for her starring role as Quinn King in the drama series Unreal (2015–18), for which she won a Critics' Choice Television Award and received a nomination for the Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series. Zimmer is further known for her roles in various television series, such as Entourage, Boston Legal, Love Bites, Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D., and House of Cards.
